          "text": "​​@dn30001Nope, not exactly. If you mean forgotten Xmascakes, that's when they are past the 25th... 🎉 But I don't care, honestly! 😂\n There are beautiful Showa Onas with beautiful babies at the age of 35 too. ❤ \nBTW: \nHas anyone out there ever seen an ugly japanese baby? 😂 One which is not looking like a cuddly peluche? ❤ \nTheir girls are kawaii from scratch on, they start being kawaii at birth and it seems to go on until menopause or even beyond it.❤\nYeah beyond it, cuz I have seen a video with a japanese Lady pretending to be 50, but she got no wrinkles, not a single gray hair and all in all she looks like yobai could get her pregnant instantly... ❤\nThe strange thing is, she also says she is divorced, which would be more typical for a Lady after climacterion has hit her femininity. So if she acknowledges her divorce publicly and worldwide, she is at least not the typical liar...\nNow why does she look rather like the daughter of a 50 years old Lady ? ❤\nI don't get it... 😮 It remains an unsolved mystery! But a rather appealing one... ❤",
